Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.36,0:00:38.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.41,0:00:41.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:18.00,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暖和的溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.92,0:02:26.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都受到鈴她們的照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.30,0:02:28.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做為男人真沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.19,0:02:31.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  那是劍道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.22,0:02:34.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是劍道  是爺爺教我的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.12,0:02:37.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺說男人就應該保護女人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.27,0:02:46.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人必須要保護女孩不可嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.25,0:02:52.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說了什麼奇怪的話了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.26,0:02:55.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  這個島上沒有男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:02:57.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以感覺有點難理解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.89,0:03:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於不知道男人的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.62,0:03:01.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從不依靠男人的鈴來說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.60,0:03:03.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算知道字面意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.67,0:03:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也無法真正理解吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.93,0:03:19.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.85,0:03:21.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在鈴遇到危機的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.82,0:03:24.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我能展現出男孩氣概的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.29,0:03:26.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她應該就能理解我的話的意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.33,0:03:36.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說如此  也許鈴比我還要有力氣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.24,0:03:39.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要稍微休息一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.68,0:03:40.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.71,0:03:41.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.89,0:04:00.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.08,0:04:07.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地震  我討厭地震
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.30,0:04:11.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  別再搖我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.81,0:04:17.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗澡  洗澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.04,0:04:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和行人一起洗就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.54,0:04:30.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.03,0:04:33.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴　怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.66,0:04:38.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  浴室乾了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.43,0:04:43.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.28,0:04:49.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全島的浴室居然都停了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.85,0:04:52.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說  島上所有的浴室都是溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:54.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一事實才更加讓人吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.28,0:04:56.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:04:57.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.65,0:04:58.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧拜託了小凜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.69,0:05:02.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡 不用謝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.58,0:05:02.14,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼  疼  疼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.85,0:05:04.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,釘子？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.06,0:05:07.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀  手又滑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.30,0:05:08.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能會滑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.69,0:05:09.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.05,0:05:11.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是對姐姐大人下手的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.01,0:05:13.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會輕易饒你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.45,0:05:24.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.58,0:05:30.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.86,0:05:37.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.95,0:05:39.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的兩位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.01,0:05:40.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫點忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:45.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  等一下我當然會幫助行人大人洗澡的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.44,0:05:46.20,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.27,0:05:50.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從頭到腳趾任何能洗的地方都不會放過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.37,0:05:51.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.11,0:05:53.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人真狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.49,0:06:02.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾音就去燒水吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:07.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燒水  燒水  燒水…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.88,0:06:09.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樂…樂意之極
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.09,0:06:18.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我要…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.97,0:06:26.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水溫正好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.09,0:06:28.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害  厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.27,0:06:35.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.08,0:06:37.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.68,0:06:53.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾音能再暖一點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.70,0:06:58.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.57,0:07:01.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:07.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託  拜託  拜託  拜託…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右邊安全  左邊安全
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.25,0:07:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.78,0:07:47.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈  真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.78,0:07:51.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既打水  又劈柴燒火
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.28,0:07:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗澡都那麼辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.53,0:07:56.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.65,0:07:59.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是無法想像一個按鈕就能解決的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.98,0:08:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.41,0:08:02.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.34,0:08:03.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水溫好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.16,0:08:07.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看的一清二楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:09.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.48,0:08:12.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.46,0:08:16.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.06,0:08:19.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作之後  本想洗個澡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:21.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到沒有水了  真是吃了一驚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:24.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  全島的溫泉居然都停水了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.92,0:08:26.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是什麼原因
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:28.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然和地震有什麼關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:31.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的好劇烈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.43,0:08:34.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天開始就要鬱悶了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.48,0:08:38.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在無法想像沒有溫泉的生活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.69,0:08:40.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.60,0:08:43.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實不用每天都要洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.36,0:08:46.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用濕毛巾擦洗身體
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.29,0:08:48.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或在海中洗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.05,0:08:50.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方法有很多…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.08,0:08:55.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了什麼不能說的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.35,0:08:57.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常不好的衛生狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.68,0:08:59.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不把汗水洗掉會很不舒服的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.99,0:09:02.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人大人不潔淨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.48,0:09:05.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是不洗澡  飯都吃不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.82,0:09:07.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且進到海裡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.38,0:09:09.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會因為鹽變得粘乎乎的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:11.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.14,0:09:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用男人的標準來考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:15.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不合適的發言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.24,0:09:19.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  明天開始洗澡該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.75,0:09:22.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然想一早就去修
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.36,0:09:26.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這週可是從早到晚都有大量的工作要做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:49.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對女孩來說  洗澡真重要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.56,0:09:56.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  讓我來助你們一臂之力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.48,0:10:06.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  行人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.38,0:10:10.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看溫泉的情況  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.70,0:10:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沿這個上去就能達到溫泉的源頭了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.66,0:10:35.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對有恐高症的我來說還真辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.71,0:10:51.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然又這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:53.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得才上去的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.97,0:11:13.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.18,0:11:17.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.31,0:11:24.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不單救了我  還送我上來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.25,0:11:25.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.19,0:11:26.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.33,0:11:27.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是吃一驚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.37,0:11:29.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和小鷹在早晨散步的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.45,0:11:31.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人忽然從天而降了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.01,0:11:33.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從天而降…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.61,0:11:34.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.51,0:11:35.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面就交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.23,0:11:38.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傍晚的時候溫泉就會恢復原樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.58,0:11:39.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.18,0:11:42.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  沒有澡洗真痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.29,0:11:45.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凜  工作那邊沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.18,0:11:47.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.94,0:11:50.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說讓我徹底修好才回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.54,0:11:52.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:53.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.56,0:11:56.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.17,0:11:57.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.22,0:11:59.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.96,0:12:08.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是沙土把溫泉給堵住了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.91,0:12:11.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把大家帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.28,0:12:13.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.78,0:12:16.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.54,0:12:22.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好深啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.84,0:12:24.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺有點悶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.07,0:12:27.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  因為這下面是溫泉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.92,0:12:29.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.92,0:12:37.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好燙 好燙 好燙…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.30,0:12:40.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.21,0:12:44.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.73,0:12:50.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.26,0:13:00.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二  一  二…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:07.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.88,0:13:08.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.34,0:13:12.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.85,0:13:14.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何況又是在窄小的地方作業
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.63,0:13:18.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也脫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.35,0:13:23.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就涼爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.24,0:13:29.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這邊反而身體又熱了許多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.38,0:13:35.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該已經挖了許多  還沒出來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.53,0:13:37.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該馬上就出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.34,0:13:40.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫泉不會乾枯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.47,0:13:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:44.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  只是假設而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.61,0:13:46.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.21,0:13:49.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  再挖一下就會出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.57,0:13:52.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸豬排  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.13,0:14:10.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地…地震？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.26,0:14:10.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.70,0:14:14.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公子  鈴  快抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.04,0:14:29.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.50,0:14:36.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.01,0:14:38.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.67,0:14:50.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  炸豬排
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.26,0:14:52.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.08,0:14:54.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.47,0:14:56.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是比剛才那裡更深的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.85,0:15:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那種井下居然有這樣的洞窟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.15,0:15:03.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之從下來的井口出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.41,0:15:07.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個在我們掉下來之後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.58,0:15:10.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像被封住了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.55,0:15:14.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼不是出不去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.32,0:15:15.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.91,0:15:23.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  有風在流動就是說明與外界相通
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.45,0:15:24.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.52,0:15:30.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.55,0:15:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.95,0:15:39.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能站起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.89,0:15:41.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.17,0:15:44.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受傷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.83,0:15:46.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.55,0:15:47.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.16,0:16:12.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.64,0:16:15.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別勉強  快  去找出口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.94,0:16:35.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是出口
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.09,0:16:37.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.19,0:16:42.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  那麼高的地方要怎麼出去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.65,0:16:49.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快想想  行人  絕對要救出鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.65,0:17:01.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以等等嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.64,0:17:03.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.49,0:17:09.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水有點溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.34,0:17:16.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好燙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.63,0:17:18.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.95,0:17:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這石頭把溫泉堵住了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.90,0:17:26.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人要怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.25,0:17:29.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能把溫泉口稍微打開一點的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:31.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為裡面的水壓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.11,0:17:32.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穴口應該會一口氣被衝破
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.37,0:17:36.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湧出的溫泉會把我們一口氣沖起來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.39,0:17:37.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫泉也能復活了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.81,0:17:38.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正所謂一石二鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.20,0:17:54.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.17,0:18:16.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.74,0:18:31.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.94,0:18:37.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.77,0:18:40.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好燙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.60,0:18:41.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.49,0:18:48.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.20,0:19:30.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.52,0:19:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.87,0:19:57.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼…可能放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.39,0:20:02.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.74,0:20:04.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.45,0:20:17.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著啊  公子  鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.90,0:20:26.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.75,0:20:33.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一件事解決了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.90,0:20:35.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.82,0:20:38.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  你這笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.36,0:20:41.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在救到我之前  就會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.26,0:20:42.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這麼誇張吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.91,0:20:46.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是行人也受了許多傷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.35,0:20:48.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.60,0:20:53.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然男人就應該保護女人的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.55,0:20:57.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人必須保護女人…？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.38,0:21:01.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  說了你也不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.05,0:21:04.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.88,0:21:06.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.86,0:21:08.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.44,0:21:11.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.58,0:21:14.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺很開心  也許
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.30,0:21:18.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.36,0:22:50.98,biaoti2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H579A4F}「喵？師傅大人」\N「好想賞櫻花」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.43,0:23:00.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛  痛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.58,0:23:02.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷口又裂開了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.13,0:23:07.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  我進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.14,0:23:15.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在行人那邊要帶這種東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.95,0:23:20.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混浴的時候就必須要圍浴巾的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.13,0:23:24.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正能和行人一起洗  算了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.58,0:23:26.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下總算能安心點
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.06,0:23:29.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼洗身體吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.67,0:23:31.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.59,0:23:34.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是沒有意義了嗎
